---
title: Swirled White Chocolate-Cranberry Tart Serves 2 | with Graham Cracker Crust
description: Creamy white chocolate and tart cranberry spread are a match made in heaven when it comes to this easy and decadent dessert. Encased in a buttery brown sugar-graham cracker crumb crust, it's the perfect post-dinner treat!
